16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_CSYNC_62_C

21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_csync(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(rdclass);
29 UNUSED(origin);
30 UNUSED(options);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 /* Serial. */
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
35 false));
36 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
37
38 /* Flags. */
39 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
40 false));
41 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
42 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
43 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
44
45 /* Type Map */
46 return (typemap_fromtext(lexer, target, true));
47}
48
49static inline isc_result_t
50totext_csync(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
51 unsigned long num;
52 char buf[sizeof("0123456789")]; /* Also TYPE65535 */
53 isc_region_t sr;
54
55 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
56 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 6);
57
58 UNUSED(tctx);
59
60 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
61
62 num = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
63 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
64 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", num);
65 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
66
67 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
68
69 num = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
70 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
71 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", num);
72 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
73
74 /*
75 * Don't leave a trailing space when there's no typemap present.
76 */
77 if (sr.length > 0) {
78 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
79 }
80 return (typemap_totext(&sr, NULL, target));
81}
82
83static /* inline */ isc_result_t
84fromwire_csync(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
85 isc_region_t sr;
86
87 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
88
89 UNUSED(type);
90 UNUSED(rdclass);
91 UNUSED(options);
92 UNUSED(dctx);
93
94 /*
95 * Serial + Flags
96 */
97 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
98 if (sr.length < 6)
99 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
100
101 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 6));
102 isc_buffer_forward(source, 6);
103 isc_region_consume(&sr, 6);
104
105 RETERR(typemap_test(&sr, true));
106
107 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
108 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
109 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
110}
111
112static inline isc_result_t
113towire_csync(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
114
115 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
116 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 6);
117
118 UNUSED(cctx);
119
120 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
121}

123static inline int
124compare_csync(ARGS_COMPARE) {
125 isc_region_t r1;
126 isc_region_t r2;
127
128 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
129 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
130 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
131 REQUIRE(rdata1->length >= 6);
132 REQUIRE(rdata2->length >= 6);
133
134 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
135 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
136 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
137}
138
139static inline isc_result_t
140fromstruct_csync(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
141 dns_rdata_csync_t *csync = source;
142 isc_region_t region;
143
144 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
145 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
146 REQUIRE(csync->common.rdtype == type);
147 REQUIRE(csync->common.rdclass == rdclass);
148 REQUIRE(csync->typebits != NULL || csync->len == 0);
149
150 UNUSED(type);
151 UNUSED(rdclass);
152
153 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(csync->serial, target));
154 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(csync->flags, target));
155
156 region.base = csync->typebits;
157 region.length = csync->len;
158 RETERR(typemap_test(&region, true));
159 return (mem_tobuffer(target, csync->typebits, csync->len));
160}
161
162static inline isc_result_t
163tostruct_csync(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
164 isc_region_t region;
165 dns_rdata_csync_t *csync = target;
166
167 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
168 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
169 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
170
171 csync->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
172 csync->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
173 ISC_LINK_INIT(&csync->common, link);
174
175 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
176
177 csync->serial = uint32_fromregion(&region);
178 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
179
180 csync->flags = uint16_fromregion(&region);
181 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
182
183 csync->len = region.length;
184 csync->typebits = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
185 if (csync->typebits == NULL)
186 goto cleanup;
187
188 csync->mctx = mctx;
189 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
190
191 cleanup:
192 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
193}
194
195static inline void
196freestruct_csync(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
197 dns_rdata_csync_t *csync = source;
198
199 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
200 REQUIRE(csync->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_csync);
201
202 if (csync->mctx == NULL)
203 return;
204
205 if (csync->typebits != NULL)
206 isc_mem_free(csync->mctx, csync->typebits);
207 csync->mctx = NULL;
208}

211additionaldata_csync(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
212 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
213
214 UNUSED(rdata);
215 UNUSED(add);
216 UNUSED(arg);
217
218 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
219}

221static inline isc_result_t
222digest_csync(ARGS_DIGEST) {
223 isc_region_t r;
224
225 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
226
227 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
228 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
229}

256static inline int
257casecompare_csync(ARGS_COMPARE) {
258 isc_region_t region1;
259 isc_region_t region2;
260
261 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
262 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
263 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_csync);
264 REQUIRE(rdata1->length >= 6);
265 REQUIRE(rdata2->length >= 6);
266
267 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
268 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
269 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
270}
